@startuml PB3Architecture
title Aiwa PB-3 Replacement Battery Architecture
footer Â©2025 Sean Donnellan
skinparam backgroundColor #fff/aaf
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing 1

rectangle "Printed Shell" {
  component "Connector\n(2-pin + NTC)" as Connector
}

component "LiFePO4 Cell\n(1S 1500 mAh)" as Cell
component "BMS\n(OCP/OVP/UVP)" as BMS
component "NTC Sensor" as NTC
component "Boost Converter\n4.05 V @ 1 A" as Boost
component "Charge Pads" as Charge
component "Host Deck" as Host

Cell --> BMS : charge/discharge
BMS --> Boost : protected supply
Boost --> Connector : regulated 4.0 V
BMS --> Charge : bypass for CC/CV charging
NTC --> Connector : temp sense lead
Connector --> Host : power + telemetry
Host --> Charge : legacy charger (optional)

@enduml
